{"tid":2156148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上月訪港旅客續跌　整體人次按年下跌逾99%","createTime":"2020-08-14T09:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T09:19:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4897c64f0208cc957d8cb0db8244a814f61279b3","tid":2156148,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543725-20200814.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543725-20200814.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcSBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=c8171f5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543725-20200814.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5ec3cd99\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543725-20200814.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港旅遊發展局公布7月初步訪港數字為20600人次，每日平均人次約660，整體按年下跌99.6%。<br />\n<br />\n在7月份，內地訪港旅客人次約有5700，按年下跌99.9%；非內地旅客人次亦下跌近99%，只有14800多人次；而1至7月訪港旅客人次，整體下跌91%。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局主席彭耀佳表示，環球疫情反覆，旅發局一直積極和業界保持緊密溝通，自3月以來舉行近90場業界網上會議，有約1萬位內地及海外的業界參與。旅發局亦邀請本地旅行社、航空公司、酒店和景點代表分享，讓業界對疫情發展、防疫工作、旅發局復甦和支援有更具體的了解。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局由本月起，會繼續舉行至少另外45場網上業界會議，預計會有4500名業界參與。局方會與政府和業界合作，積極籌備促銷宣傳計劃。"},{"pid":"7a17bc364612b41b3a8d3ee37308f9d344c21591","tid":2156148,"uid":41087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"點解仲有1%<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b26b5ee43666d15473ba28cbd4ecee2d200aa21","tid":2156148,"uid":244809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a17bc364612b41b3a8d3ee37308f9d344c21591","tid":2156148,"uid":41087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"點解仲有1%<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"仲有商務簽證"},{"pid":"33a14256eed847aeb6c995fc0f6daf